                  </hi>. I am master of the schooner <hi rend="italic">Vigilant.</hi> On the 26th of Dec. she was lying at Simmons'-wharf, Tooley-street—the prisoner was my apprentice—I missed him on that day, and not ten minutes after he was gone I missed out of the cabin two pairs of canvass trowsers—they have not been found—I had four men on board beside the prisoner.</p>
